    "# Star-Infant ARC-AGI-3 Submission\n",
    "\n",
    "**Solver:** ActionEffectTracker — learns from action effects, uses Infant perception.\n",
    "\n",
    "Uses:\n",
    "1. **Infant** — CNN-based object extraction from grid images\n",
    "2. **ActionEffectTracker** — learns which actions produce useful state changes\n",
    "\n",
    "**How to run:**\n",
    "- Add `ARC_API_KEY` to Kaggle Secrets (get from https://arcprize.org/api)\n",
    "- Dataset `zacharymaronek/arc-star-model` will be downloaded automatically\n",
    "- Run all cells\n",
    "\n",
    "**NOTE:** Star KG runs locally. For Kaggle GPU without Star, the solver uses ActionEffectTracker + Infant perception."
   ]
  },
